{
    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a streamlined body painted in glossy white. The car features a sharply contoured hood with a black vent, angular headlights, and a wide front grille. Its roof and windows are tinted in a deep red, contrasting with the white exterior. The side profile reveals aerodynamic lines, black multi-spoke alloy wheels, and a subtle side vent behind the front wheel. At the rear, the car has a pronounced rear window, integrated taillights, and a subtle rear spoiler. The overall design emphasizes speed, performance, and modern aesthetics, typical of high-end sports cars.",
